body:
Music: BTS – Boy With Luv Ft. Halsey

Download new song by BTS – Boy With Luv Ft. Halsey

“Boy With Luv” is a new tune by South Korean boy band “BTS” featuring “Halsey“.

A funky dance track that opens up with woozy synths and rollicking strings.

BTS, also known as the Bangtan Boys, is a seven-member South Korean boy band formed by Big Hit Entertainment in 2013.

The name became a backronym for Beyond the Scene in July 2017.

body:
Reaction while listening to Persona

I legit teared up while listening to Mikrokosmos and from there it’s being an emotional rollercoaster.

And I’m on the edge of tears with Jamais Vu. What a new, amazing unit.

DIONYSUS IS A BOP, OH SH- It’s pure chaotic energy and I live for it. It’s also fitting since I’m currently reading The Secret History, lol.

Gosh, how much I respect and admire those 7 men.

summary: About hour ago "Boy With Luv" was played by the biggest radio station in Poland. It's such a big deal because despite the fact...
body:
About hour ago “Boy With Luv” was played by the biggest radio station in Poland. It’s such a big deal because despite the fact that BTS albums are distributed here our boys aren’t in mainstream. This is a chance to change that, I can’t believe that!
